                        iteration vs legacy 10-year procurement cycles. </p>
                    <p class="stock-description"> <strong>Why it's a buy (when public):</strong> $1B+ revenue (2025) up
                        from $150M (2023) = 200%+ growth. DoD contracts for border surveillance ($250M), counter-drone
                        ($500M), submarine autonomy ($200M). Winning multi-billion contracts reserved for primes
                        (Lockheed, Raytheon). TAM: $50B+ autonomous systems market. IPO expected 2027 at $25-40B
                        valuation. </p>
                    <p class="stock-description"> <strong>Risks:</strong> Private (not investable yet). Unproven at
                        scale (small contracts relative to LMT/RTX). Regulatory hurdles for autonomous weapons. </p>
                    <span class="conviction-level conviction-watch">WATCH LIST ‚Äî IPO 2027 EXTREME BUY</span>
